data.name: g_license.Text
data.value:
NoEye is the software used in online multiplayer games that actively prevents BattlEye to protect and scan for cheats on BattlEye-protected servers.
In order to achieve goal NoEye installs a system service that is only active while BattlEye is running. The NoEye system service also injects a dll into the service.
While due to it's nature NoEye needs to have access to great parts of your system, it ensures that your privacy is not violated. NoEye is neither interested in your personal data(documents, passwords, credit card details, etc.) nor any other information that is private to you as an indvidual. Everything that NoEye does is solely aimed at archieving its goal of preventing BattlEye to detect cheats and scan your system.
To install NoEye and be able to play on BattlEye-protected-servers without BattlEye, please click "Install" below. Otherwise click "Uninstall" to remove NoEye.
